        "text": "The app shall allow the user to switch on the Presenter light of a selected connected appliance using the app's Presenter light control.",
        "happyFlow": "The user selects the Presenter light control for a connected appliance, chooses the on state, and the app sends the on command and shows the resulting on state after confirmation.",
        "alternativeFlows": [
